title: The Best of Government Issue - The Mystic Years
description:
Early years of G.I. This band was great in the Eighties they must have played CBGB&#039;s 100 times in 85-86 and people reallly knew how to dance back then none of this Moshing Bullshit it was Mother Fucking slam dancing and if you got out of step you got beat down like a Bitch!
This band has that Classic DC Hardcore sound you know the shit you crave 
Once again I will say it Good Music for shitty peaople!

Rocktookmehere

I would like like to thank Tommy Scum for providing with access to his collection what he don&#039;t know won&#039;t hurt him!
